<p>Hello <%= @student.name.split(" ").first %>,</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder that the class you registered for, <%= @course.title %>, is happening tomorrow. We hope you're all ready and excited. Here are some handy details for you:</p>

<p>
When: <%= @course.starts_at.strftime("%a %b %d, %Y") %> at <%= @course.starts_at.strftime("%l:%M%p") %> - <%= @course.ends_at.strftime("%l:%M%p") %><br>
Where: <%= @course.place_name %> - <%= @course.address %>, <%= @course.city.name %>, <%= @course.city.state %>, <%= @course.zip %><br>
<%= "Direction: #{@course.directions}" if @course.directions.present? %>
</p>

<p>Got questions? You can message your teacher at <%= @url %></p>
